about.summary: The fastest markdown parser in pure Python

name: mistune
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.7.3" %}

package:
  name: mistune
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: mistune-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/lepture/mistune/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c4f391e61d3b5e8fbb112669a5c6960fb04b71b61d35f0f09a201809545b1676

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  requires:
    - python
    - nose
  imports:
    - mistune
  commands:
    - cd "{{ SRC_DIR }}"
    - python setup.py -q nosetests

about:
  home: https://github.com/lepture/mistune
  license:  BSD 3-clause
  summary: The fastest markdown parser in pure Python

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pelson
    - bollwyvl
